data.description: This charming home features a fenced backyard perfect for privacy and outdoor enjoyment. The lower level offers spacious living with a cozy fireplace. Conveniently located, this home is just a few doors away from the Southridge Meadow neighborhood park. It’s also within reasonable distance to the Chalco Hills Recreation Area and the new Prairie Queen Recreation Area. For shopping options, you can explore the LaVista Shopping areas near Cabela’s. With excellent interstate access and being part of the Millard Schools district, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Book your appt today! Appointment is required.
